  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/27/htc-sells-all-beats-electronics-shares/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/09/dsc0023.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 399px; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n不知不觉，原来 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2011/08/11/htc-to-buy-a-chunk-of-beats-electronics-keep-dr-dre-in-a-lab-w/\"><span class=\"s1\">HTC </span>和 <span class=\"s1\">Beats </span>的关系</a>已经持续两年了。而经过了这么一段日子，看来 <span class=\"s1\">Beats </span>方面也想要一点转变。继一年前<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2012/07/22/beats-htc-realign-business-agreement/\">回购了 <span class=\"s1\">HTC </span>手上一半的股份</a>后，我们也听到了这家耳机厂商有意停止合作的传闻。到一个月后的今天，这个传闻终于得到证实了。根据 <span class=\"s1\">Nasdaq </span>的消息，<span class=\"s1\">Beats </span>决定以 <span class=\"s1\">2.65 </span>亿美金（约 <span class=\"s1\">16.2 </span>亿人民币）将 <span class=\"s1\">HTC </span>手上的股份全数回购。<span class=\"s1\"> HTC </span>方面则没有说明这次交易是否和<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/30/htc-q3-2013-forecast/\">财务危机</a>有关，只重申和 <span class=\"s1\">Beats </span>之间仍然是紧密的合作关系，而相关交易则会在本年底前完成。那既然还是合作关系，那 <span class=\"s1\">Beats Audio </span>应该还会留在 <span class=\"s1\">HTC </span>的手机上了吧？<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/09/27/htc-sells-all-beats-electronics-shares/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.nasdaq.com/article/beats-electronics-buys-back-htc-stake-in-company-for-us265-million-20130927-00062\">Nasdaq</a>、<a href=\"http://www.nasdaq.com/article/beats-electronics-buys-back-htc-stake-in-company-for-us265-million-20130927-00062\">Dow Jones</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/27/htc-sells-all-beats-electronics-shares/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20731589/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/27/htc-sells-all-beats-electronics-shares/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
